						order to get it working:
					</p>
					<hr>

					<ol>
						<li>
							Register for a
							<a href="https://foursquare.com/developers/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
								<strong>Foursquare Developer Account {{> svgExternal}}</strong>
							</a> and create a new project.
						</li>
						<li>
							Create a Service API Key, then fill in the <em>Client ID</em>, <em>Client Secret</em>, and
							<em>Push Secret</em> fields below.
						</li>
						<li>
							Set the <em>Redirect URL</em> to<br>
							<small><code>{{externalRoot}}/api/swarm/callback</code></small>
						</li>
						<li>
							In the Foursquare project settings page, scroll down to find the <em>Push API</em> section.
							Set <em>Push Notifications</em> to "Push checkins by this project's users", then use the
							device picker below to grab a <em>Push URL</em>, and set it on the project settings page.
						</li>
						<li>
							Once you've saved your changes on this page, visit the
							<a href="{{externalRoot}}/api/swarm/login" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
								<strong>Swarm login page {{> svgExternal}}</strong>
							</a> to register your Swarm account with this server.
						</li>
						<li>
							Finally, visit your
							<a href="https://foursquare.com/settings" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
								<strong>Foursquare Settings page {{> svgExternal}}</strong>
							</a> and copy the <em>User ID</em> into the User ID field below.
						</li>
						<li>
							⚠️ <strong>Note:</strong> You may need to add a billing method to your account in order to
